{"parentUuid": "bb5bfbf2-c480-49db-b0c2-8e8fd7d72d6f", "isSidechain": false, "message": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-6", "id": "msg_b78b70da-027", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Running `echo` to check."}, {"type": "tool_use", "id": "toolu_0ee04b4e-8477-4f", "name": "Bash", "input": {"command": "echo $TERM && tmux display-message -p '#{client-termfeatures}'", "description": "zsh-autosuggestions slow in tmux"}}], "stop_reason": "tool_use", "usage": {"input_tokens": 1075, "output_tokens": 227, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 18509}}, "requestId": "req_5930c427-94d", "type": "assistant", "uuid": "c10b8e1c-6d5b-469c-8ac9-67e68a7c9500", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T16:00:35.000Z", "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/dotfiles", "sessionId": "9b2a14da-f921-4f5e-9fb5-ee6b3e0f303a", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
{"parentUuid": "c10b8e1c-6d5b-469c-8ac9-67e68a7c9500", "isSidechain": false, "type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "tool_result", "tool_use_id": "toolu_0ee04b4e-8477-4f", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "screen-256color\n*256\\:RGB"}]}]}, "uuid": "af2400bd-161c-477e-9443-cb6419b4d68d", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T16:00:37.000Z", "isMeta": true, "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/dotfiles", "sessionId": "9b2a14da-f921-4f5e-9fb5-ee6b3e0f303a", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
{"parentUuid": "af2400bd-161c-477e-9443-cb6419b4d68d", "isSidechain": false, "message": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-6", "id": "msg_175c3a41-fbb", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Two things conspire: (1) `screen-256color` doesn't advertise the BCE (background-color-erase) capability, so the plugin's redraw path can't optimize partial line clears and ends up rewriting the whole prompt. (2) tmux's input event loop adds a small RTT to every keystroke when the suggestion redraw triggers. Fixes: set `TERM=tmux-256color` (you'll need `infocmp tmux-256color` to confirm it's available on your system) and add `set -as terminal-features ',xterm*:RGB'` in your tmux.conf. Plugin lag drops below the perceptible threshold for me."}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "usage": {"input_tokens": 675, "output_tokens": 295, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}}, "requestId": "req_e8339dcd-279", "type": "assistant", "uuid": "7b40dc12-b03d-4769-8dff-f0a2b1583863", "timestamp": "2026-04-24T16:00:43.000Z", "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/dotfiles", "sessionId": "9b2a14da-f921-4f5e-9fb5-ee6b3e0f303a", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
